 in the GCL was 12,254.17 \u00b1 660.39 and that of the optic nerve axons was 5,179.04 \u00b1 208.00 in the R. ferrumequinum retina. The total number of melanopsin-IR cells was 819.74 \u00b1 52.03. The ipRGCs constituted approximately 15.83% of the total RGC population. This study demonstrated that the nocturnal microbat, R. ferrumequinum, has a much higher density of melanopsin-IR cells than documented in diurnal animals.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Jeong, Mi-Jin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kim, Hang-Gu", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jeon, Chang-Jin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Badea, Tudor C.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/eb76ca94034c4f9fe056c765a5c6cd32", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/1ed3c628caa6d2368a79f4e7813463587edac7a2c1461a5d202ac685ab4ec043", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/B7FW8UFV", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/B7FW8UFV", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/b0f1c2e72a7eac4216929e66ae3cc77a!/b329237-331699", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "e0190435", "title": "PLOS ONE", "volume": "13"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/eb76ca94034c4f9fe